-- Casino Shareholders Remove Diniz From Board of Directors
-- B y   A l b e r t i n a   T o r s o l i
-- 2012-05-12T15:25:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-12/casino-shareholders-remove-diniz-from-board-of-directors.html
Shareholders of  Casino Guichard-
Perrachon SA (CO) , a French supermarket, yesterday approved the
removal of Abilio Diniz from the company’s board of directors,
according to a recording of the annual general meeting on the
company’s website.  The retailer had recommended not renewing his mandate in a
March 29 statement.  Diniz remains chairman of Cia Brasileira de Distribuicao
 Grupo Pao de Acucar ’s,  Brazil ’s largest retailer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
